snippet.title: Friday Night Funkin' VS Homr V2 FULL WEEK | Homer Simpson, Bart, Marge & Peter Griffin (FNF Mod)
snippet.description:
Friday Night Funkin' VS Homr 2.0 for the PC in 2160p Ultra HD, but this time we battle Homr and the Simpsons family (a parody version of them + Peter Griffin) | BTW it's a joke mod!
DonAlgo - Owner: https://youtu.be/Qi67Fez7GK8

This is a funny joke mod, but the songs here are pretty good. The sprites are purposely low quality to make it funnier and etc. Anyway, the joke mods are usually the ones with the most banger songs. This update includes Homer Simpson, Bart Simpson, Marge Simpson, Family Guy Peter Griffin, and Soy Homero Chino, but poor Lisa and Maggie are not included. Will Boyfriend and Girlfriend defeat the simpsons or will bf and gf be defeated by them?

VS Friday Night Funkin' Vs Homr 2.0 Mod Download:
https://gamebanana.com/mods/355550

Game Note by VS Homr: This is the VS HOMR mod, a full week and 3 songs in Freeplay
